{"tid":2174032,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"諗咗好耐，終於諗到點解林鄭特別憎恨醫護…","createTime":"2020-08-25T15:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T17:27:27.000Z","uid":152123,"like":43,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b6db8d575e6c95b1eaea567f493bf61c75453db7","tid":2174032,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:31:58.000Z","msg":"你諗下 當年林鄭年年都考第一<br />\n但佢最後竟然唔係讀醫或者法律<br />\n而係soc sci！<br />\n以佢咁好勝嘅性格 會似係報呢啲科、一心貢獻社會嘅人咩？<br />\n的確 反送中至今 醫護係好黃<br />\n但同時其實都有好多行業好黃 包括律師<br />\n但相比醫護 唔見得林鄭特別憎恨律師<br />\n反而處處針對醫護 係全方位咁樣針對醫護<br />\n我有理由相信根本林鄭當年被醫學院拒收懷恨在心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5ca459c692ef741e2caf6583c14df316693f68","tid":2174032,"uid":249885,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:33:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac5c4b6c5ccc911c943113fb3883999c62d03b98","tid":2174032,"uid":152123,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"9d5ca459c692ef741e2caf6583c14df316693f68","tid":2174032,"uid":249885,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:33:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"佢份人好撚小氣 自尊心咁高<br />\n連中學考第一都可以講到過半百<br />\n有可能係被醫學院拒絕咗懷恨在心"},{"pid":"89404d167213c644945545f16d5aa61f88b48758","tid":2174032,"uid":21545,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:35:10.000Z","msg":"讀文科點考med school"},{"pid":"8d7466ca6f7d76c104ab5117f939e394967b0be7","tid":2174032,"uid":276440,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T15:36:52.000Z","msg":"佢預科讀文科，大學點會讀到醫科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af781c031238fcc2c9315f273f60026f7fc5046","tid":2174032,"uid":